    "We employ Mask2former (Cheng et al. 2022) as our decoder, which is a highly efficient and effective algorithm for semantic segmentation tasks.",
    "For backbone, we utilize the Dinov2-Large (Oquab et al. 2023) model to extract features, which are subsequently utilized as input for the Mask2former.",
    "During training, we utilize AdamW (Loshchilov and Hutter 2019) as the optimizer, with a learning rate of 1e-5 for the backbone, 1e-4 for the decoder, and 1e-4 for the relevant parameters in PEFT.",
    "Within the DACS training framework, we set λ da to 0.5.",
